151
00:17:08,231 --> 00:17:09,349
A while ago,

152
00:17:10,299 --> 00:17:12,367
people had to abandon their cars and walk

153
00:17:13,111 --> 00:17:15,262
because of the heavy snow.

154
00:17:15,841 --> 00:17:17,289
I remember.

155
00:17:17,950 --> 00:17:20,514
I also had to leave my car
on Yeongdong Bridge and walk.

156
00:17:21,093 --> 00:17:22,789
And I suddenly thought,

157
00:17:23,905 --> 00:17:26,345
"If the earth just stopped
for a while like this,

158
00:17:28,909 --> 00:17:31,349
I would just keep walking
until I reached Sanpo."

159
00:17:33,541 --> 00:17:37,304
"If I take the shortest route,
it should be about 28km."

160
00:17:37,801 --> 00:17:39,702
"I'd be there by dawn."

161
00:17:40,281 --> 00:17:44,996
