figuring out where to make turns.

162
00:17:45,741 --> 00:17:46,899
It was funny

163
00:17:47,478 --> 00:17:50,786
that I was thinking about walking there
if the Earth stopped,

164
00:17:50,869 --> 00:17:52,936
when I could just drive there.

165
00:18:00,215 --> 00:18:01,414
Do you remember

166
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:06,005
