Was I an asshole, too?

219
00:23:07,626 --> 00:23:08,991
Not anymore.

220
00:23:10,892 --> 00:23:12,589
You called in the end.

221
00:23:16,393 --> 00:23:18,461
But I was an asshole till yesterday?

222
00:23:48,857 --> 00:23:50,098
Welcome.

223
00:23:59,568 --> 00:24:01,223
-Thank you.
